&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: large;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Faça comentários, &lt;a href="http://www.trezentos.blog.br/?p=5484)." target="_blank"&gt;clicando aqui&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jan 2011 16:53:07 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/carta-aberta-ao-trtrj-sobre-a-troca-de-suite-de-escritorio</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/carta-aberta-ao-trtrj-sobre-a-troca-de-suite-de-escritorio</guid></item></channel></rss>